thread.title: BRIEF-India's Syndicate Bank Posts Dec Qtr Loss

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-India's Syndicate Bank Posts Dec Qtr Loss

organizations.name: brief-india's syndicate bank posts dec qtr loss feb

text:
Feb 9 (Reuters) - Syndicate Bank Ltd:
* DEC QUARTER NET LOSS 8.70 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS PROFIT OF 935.6 MILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* DEC QUARTER INTEREST EARNED 53.76 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 55.68 BILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* DEC QUARTER PROVISIONS AND CONTINGENCIES 20.90 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 7.85 BILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* DEC QUARTER PROVISIONS FOR NPAS 19.49 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 2.33 BILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* DEC QUARTER GROSS NPA 9.62 PERCENT VERSUS 9.39 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER
* DEC QUARTER NET NPA 5.44 PERCENT VERSUS 5.76 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER Source text - bit.ly/2H21gO3 Further company coverage:
